%% Diagram: Two-pass flex layout — measure pass then layout pass
%% Type: sequence
%%{init: {'htmlLabels': false}}%%
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Parent as Flex Container
    participant A as Child A
    participant B as Child B
    participant C as Child C

    Note over Parent,C: Measure pass — find max intrinsic size
    Parent->>A: measure(available)
    A-->>Parent: intrinsic = 80
    Parent->>B: measure(available)
    B-->>Parent: intrinsic = 120
    Parent->>C: measure(available)
    C-->>Parent: intrinsic = 60
    Note over Parent: target = max(80,120,60) = 120

    Note over Parent,C: Layout pass — stretch all to target
    Parent->>A: layout(width=120)
    A-->>Parent: fragment
    Parent->>B: layout(width=120)
    B-->>Parent: fragment
    Parent->>C: layout(width=120)
    C-->>Parent: fragment

    Note over Parent: Without caching, nesting N levels = O(2^N) work.<br/>LayoutNG caches both passes keyed on parent constraints.
